      "content": "That's a good start. To make him sound even more like a man of science from that era, can you expand on it? Have him describe their physical appearance and their lifestyle in a way that contrasts their 'primitive' nature with the 'advanced' standards of Europe. He should sound like he's documenting them as a species that's just waiting to be managed.",
